echo \(dqTask complete.\(dq
\f[B]\(ga\(ga\(ga\f[R]
.EE
.PP
You can also make your flag expect a numerical value by setting its
\f[CR]type\f[R] to \f[CR]number\f[R].
\f[CR]inkjet\f[R] will automatically validate it as a number for you.
If it fails to validate, \f[CR]inkjet\f[R] will exit with a helpful
error message.
